msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/berserker.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 13 (hide armor)    \n"
"**Hit Points** 67 (9d8 + 27)    \n"
"**Speed** 30 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/berserker.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 16 (+3) | 12 (+1) | 17 (+3) | 9 (−1)  | 11 (+0) | 9 (−1)  |  \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/berserker.md:19
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Senses** passive Perception 10    \n"
"**Languages** any one language (usually Common)    \n"
"**Challenge** 2 (450 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/berserker.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Reckless.** At the start of its turn, the berserker can gain advantage on "
"all melee weapon attack rolls during that turn, but attack rolls against it "
"have advantage until the start of its next turn. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/berserker.md:24
msgid ""
"### Actions **Greataxe.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 9 (1d12 + 3) slashing damage."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/berserker.md:26
msgid ""
"### Description Hailing from uncivilized lands, unpredictable berserkers "
"come together in war parties and seek conflict wherever they can find it."
msgstr ""
